\f1\b0\fs26 \cf0 Scrivener projects aren\'92t only for storing text. Many books and long documents require a great deal of research, and you can import your research documents\'97images, PDF files, even movie and sound files\'97directly into Scrivener. So you can easily switch between your writing and a research document.\
Scrivener fully supports the iPad\'92s split screen feature, so that you can refer to information in other applications while you write. Just drag inwards from the right edge of the screen and select another app to open alongside Scrivener.\
